      "instruction": "<p>Stir in your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong>, then add the<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong> and<strong> </strong>400ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[600ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[800ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
