    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pasta has been cooking for 25 min, remove the dish from the oven</p><p>Drain your <strong>king prawns</strong>, then add them to the dish and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cover with a lid and return the dish to the oven for 4-5 min further or until the<strong> </strong>prawns are cooked through and the pasta is tender – this is your <strong>oven-baked</strong> <strong>spicy king prawn arrabbiata farfalle</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
